font-weight:bold">save money?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="59" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">A change of thi</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">s</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> kin</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">d is likely to result in changes in the behaviour of both </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">c</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">laimants</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> and </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">d</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">efendants.  Some of those changes are likely to be at a cost to the public purse.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="60" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Defendant </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">authorities will be</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> less willing to settle in response to a let</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">t</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">er before </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">claim in</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> th</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">e hope that </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">c</span><span style="font-famil